arts.ttl: Mourinho banned for three matches for bust-up with Galatasaray boss
arts.sum: Jose Mourinho has been handed a three-match ban by the Turkish Football Federation (TFF) for grabbing opposition manager Okan Buruk's face at the end of Fenerbahce's 2-1 Turkish Cup defeat against rivals Galatasaray.
